      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(3 inline comments)\n\nPatch looks good, except for minor style issues (particularly the commit summary line).\n\nIt seems that even though fsfilt_setup() always could return an error, it was never checked.  Good catch.\n\nA general question, is the MRP-118 bug (or any MRP-* bug) open for external review?  If not, it is useful to paste any relevant parts from that bug (e.g. error messages seen, etc) into the LU-836 bug for future reference, in case someone else tries to do this same thing in the future.",
